Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Paris Las Vegas
Description: This location in Las Vegas presents a half-scale replica of the Eiffel Tower which doubles as a observation deck!

Name: Griffith Observatory
Description: This landmark includes technology such as a telescope that displays images of the sun, a large and stunning tesla coil, and more!

Name: Niagra Falls
Description: Here you can view several famous, towering waterfalls along with the presented opportunity get closer to these monuments with tours!

Name: Leaning Tower of Pisa
Description: A freestanding bell tower that, as a result of an unstable foundation, gained its iconic four-degree lean than is known around the world!

Name: Sistine Chapel
Description: This famous chapel in the Vatican Museums is most known for Michelangelo's iconic painting "The Creation of Adam"!
